name: Digimon Tumblr Dashboard Icons
description:
Hey there, Digifans! This style changes the Tumblr dashboard icons to the original seven Digimon partners from the first season: Agumon, Gabumon, Biyomon, Tentomon, Palmon, Gomamon, and Patamon. The icons used are sprites from the Digimon Anode/Cathode Tamer game for the WonderSwan.

Enjoy!

user.name: Zombie-Raptor-Attack
user.about: A nerdy Tumblr user that likes making custom dashboard icons.
